{"root":{"data":{"id":"di4g3n40p7s0","created":1777344664857,"text":"Redis","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4g3u6bonc0","created":1777344680234,"text":"内存淘汰策略","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4g47jpqm00","created":1777344709342,"text":"不淘汰","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4g4c1ut9c0","created":1777344719146,"text":"新写报错，读取正常","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4g4h0lnpk0","created":1777344729954,"text":"随机淘汰","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4g4lcpzi00","created":1777344739394,"text":"从所有key中随机","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4g4o8lmu00","created":1777344745675,"text":"从带TTL的key中随机","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4g4t9a33c0","created":1777344756600,"text":"LRU近似（热门）","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4g54ijfw00","created":1777344781104,"text":"从所有key中淘汰","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4g5jdlqe80","created":1777344813458,"text":"从带TTL的key中淘汰（最常用）","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4g5vzdi8o0","created":1777344840895,"text":"LFU近似（热点）","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4g60fgs3k0","created":1777344850575,"text":"从所有key中淘汰","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4g6385a5c0","created":1777344856663,"text":"从带TTL的key中淘汰","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4g7srl7ow0","created":1777344990623,"text":"剩余TTL从小到大淘汰","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4ga0by5xs0","created":1777345163819,"text":"TTL","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4gcnsjtk00","created":1777345371618,"text":"命令","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4gcpvrsdc0","created":1777345376166,"text":"设置 （expire/pexpire）","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4gcuo1u7k0","created":1777345386583,"text":"查看（ttl/pttl）","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4gd1j10s80","created":1777345401517,"text":"取消（persist）","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4gdnbqmgg0","created":1777345448965,"text":"到期删除策略","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4gfaho15s0","created":1777345577754,"text":"惰性删除+定期删除（随机多少个，写死20个）","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4gpf71ojc0","created":1777346371637,"text":"穿透","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4gpllx1940","created":1777346385597,"text":"请求数据库中不存在的数据","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4gpyyhg000","created":1777346414655,"text":"提前校验合法性，布隆过滤器（可能不存在，一定不存在）","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4h5wv3d4o0","created":1777347663923,"text":"缓存空对象","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4h66q50t40","created":1777347685391,"text":"占内存","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4h68zcgqw0","created":1777347690302,"text":"短暂数据不一致","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4h6dueceo0","created":1777347700886,"text":"击穿","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4h6qfxo480","created":1777347728310,"text":"热点key同时查询","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4h76qr9y80","created":1777347763793,"text":"Redis侧数据永不过期，业务自己处理过期","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4h7kqx5s00","created":1777347794278,"text":"互斥锁","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4h8c0vulc0","created":1777347853653,"text":"雪崩","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4h8i9xqz40","created":1777347867261,"text":"大量缓存同一时间过期或Redis宕机","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4h9136g8g0","created":1777347908212,"text":"TTL设置分散","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4h9v629og0","created":1777347973690,"text":"Redis永不过期，异步处理过期","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4hbg3b49k0","created":1777348097600,"text":"定时任务提前处理缓存更新","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4havx1v680","created":1777348053686,"text":"宕机","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4hay8xesg0","created":1777348058757,"text":"多级缓存","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4hb1su3uw0","created":1777348066491,"text":"缓存预热","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4hcmavw1k0","created":1777348189483,"text":"Redis集群","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4ki7xybmo0","created":1777357091740,"text":"持久化","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4kicct9ug0","created":1777357101346,"text":"RDB","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4kjl8aifs0","created":1777357199028,"text":"自动触发：redis.conf里配置 save 300 10（300秒\n内有10次写操作）","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4kj8mtbcg0","created":1777357171608,"text":"手动触发：save 或者 bgsave\nbgsave流程：\n1. 父进程fork一个子进程（拥有父进程内存数据副本）\n2. 子进程遍历内存数据，写入RDB文件\n3. 子进程完成后，替换旧的RDB文件\n4. 父进程继续处理客户端请求","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4kie20t140","created":1777357105047,"text":"AOF","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4kpuwzph40","created":1777357690297,"text":"流程：\n1. 命令写入缓冲区\n2. 缓冲区数据fsync到磁盘AOF文件（always、everys\necond、no - 操作系统自己决定）\n3. 重启的时候读取命令逐条回放","layout_left_offset":{"x":-180,"y":8},"font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4ktfkhdww0","created":1777357970346,"text":"AOF 重写\n1. 父进程fork一个子进程（拥有父进程内存数据副\n本），并开启一个rewrite aof缓冲区，父进程继续处\n理并把命令同时写到rewrite aof缓冲区\n2. 遍历内存数据，生成所需最精简命令并写入一个临时\n的AOF文件\n3. 把rewrite aof缓冲区的内容再增加到aof文件\n4. 执行AOF文件rename原子替换","layout_left_offset":{"x":-87,"y":22},"font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4lm63y0680","created":1777360222316,"text":"Multi AOF","layout_left_offset":{"x":-99,"y":14},"font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4m9tammag0","created":1777362075162,"text":"RewriteAOF的问题：\n1. 内存开销（rewrite aof缓冲区数据和aof缓冲区数据\n重复）\n2. CPU开销（写rewrite aof buf文件、把buf文件附加\n到aof）\n3. 磁盘IO开销，两个buf文件的相同数据都要写到磁盘","layout_left_offset":{"x":-3,"y":26},"font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di4mh0r83mo0","created":1777362639952,"text":"MAOF方案（三种AOF文件，BASE、INCR和HISTORY）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-13,"y":58},"font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4kik3b0io0","created":1777357118185,"text":"混合持久化","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4n61s06sw0","created":1777364601280,"text":"AOF重写的第二个步骤直接生成rdb格式数据","layout_left_offset":{"x":-12,"y":75},"font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di4och4a6sg0","created":1777367925969,"text":"主从同步","layout_mind_offset":{"x":169,"y":17},"font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di4ofs8epj40","created":1777368185255,"text":"1. 建立连接（replicaof），开启同步（psync runid\n offset）\n2. 主节点响应FULLRESYNC并生成RDB快照（bgsave）\n3. 缓冲写命令（这个缓冲区每个同步连接独享一个）\n4. 发送RDB文件\n5. 从节点加载RDB\n6. 主节点发送缓冲区命令\n7. 从节点接收命令并依次执行\n以下是增量同步\n1. 主节点缓冲写命令（repl_backlog，共享一个）\n2. 主节点发送缓冲区命令，从节点接收\n3. 从节点重放命令，并更新offset","layout_left_offset":{"x":-170,"y":99},"font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}